            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>5月15-19日，深圳市南山区控烟执法“车轮战”打响。执法队伍来到南山区亿利达大厦2栋、方大城、朗山路中公交站、网鱼网咖（深圳南山公园南路店）、南山地铁站周边餐饮5大吸烟举报“重灾区”，来了场“有求必应”的突击检查！控烟车轮战片段回放来了，一起回顾👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟进行时#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4905257260744756" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1heai3ahzagj21g80teter.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/SmETZzTGgx085Ib2zpwc01041201Ron70E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1252x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684991901&amp;ssig=4CD%2FLtu3mA&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/MrhF5hvngx085Ib1PCsE01041200Zt1O0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=832x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684991901&amp;ssig=bfMlaTkQ7b&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/PUL9H3fdgx085Ib1JCP601041200EDdz0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=624x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684991901&amp;ssig=vYB0jaSX1l&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4905257260744756&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
