            <title><![CDATA[525全国护肤日，你的护肤姿势正确吗？[思考]战“痘”大神赖维教授，移动的皮肤病“教科书”孙建方教授、深圳本地“痤疮名医”杨帆主任医师现已加入深圳护肤豪华...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[525全国护肤日，你的护肤姿势正确吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>战“痘”大神赖维教授，移动的皮肤病“教科书”孙建方教授、深圳本地“痤疮名医”杨帆主任医师现已加入深圳护肤豪华套餐<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>有皮肤问题的友友可以冲一波～<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#皮肤名医团入驻深圳#</span></a><br><blockquote> - 转发 <a href="https://weibo.com/5985797650" target="_blank">@深圳慢性病防治中心</a>: 【“一号难求”专家来了！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#皮肤名医团入驻深圳#</span></a>】你的皮肤真的健康吗？你护肤的姿势正确吗？525全国护肤日，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%A2%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%A2%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳皮肤名医天团#</span></a>正式出道！“一号难求”的专家们，现已入驻深圳市皮肤病防治研究所~皮防所集结皮肤名医孙建方、赖维、杨帆成立名医工作室，各种皮肤“疑难杂症”，手到擒来！关注<a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E7%97%85%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83">@深圳慢性病防治中心</a> 并带话题<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%BB%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#皮肤名医团入驻深圳#</span></a>，说说你最想获得哪位皮肤科名医看诊机会！我们将抽取10位小伙伴赠送免费名医挂号问诊名额！（仅限首诊免费，医药费需自理）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/006x5Npogy1heafab9rgij31u53bob2a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/006x5Npogy1heafaad6k7j31u53boe82.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/006x5Npogy1heafac72t8j31u53bo7wi.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br></blockquote>]]></description>
